<subSubSection id="50DBD8E27B338D47FF0643ABA3E2FD87" pageId="25" pageNumber="80" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="187E8B697B338D47FF0643ABA37AFE2C" blockId="25.[189,324,431,457]" box="[189,324,431,457]" pageId="25" pageNumber="80">
<heading id="43363C057B338D47FF0643ABA37AFE2C" bold="true" box="[189,324,431,457]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="25" pageNumber="80" reason="3">
<emphasis id="2AB5577B7B338D47FF0643ABA37AFE2C" bold="true" box="[189,324,431,457]" pageId="25" pageNumber="80">Comments</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="187E8B697B338D47FF0643D9A3E2FD87" blockId="25.[189,1400,477,610]" pageId="25" pageNumber="80">
This species was described for a male and the female remains unknown. Besides the 
<typeStatus id="C77A35CB7B338D47FB2743D9A738FE12" box="[1180,1286,477,503]" pageId="25" pageNumber="80">holotype</typeStatus>
, a second specimen studied was considered to be 
<taxonomicName id="DFC1F0EA7B338D47FD324005A12AFDFE" authorityName="Schrottky" authorityYear="1910" box="[649,788,513,539]" class="Insecta" family="Halictidae" genus="Sphecodes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="80" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="minarum">
<emphasis id="2AB5577B7B338D47FD324005A0A5FDFE" box="[649,667,513,539]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="80">A</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="2AB5577B7B338D47FD114006A12AFDFE" box="[682,788,514,539]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="80">minarum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, for the size, overall body sculpture and pubescence of sterna 3–5. The species is similar to 
<taxonomicName id="DFC1F0EA7B338D47FD214020A123FDDB" authority="Gonçalves &amp; Pereira, 2022" authorityName="Gonçalves &amp; Pereira" authorityYear="2022" box="[666,797,548,575]" class="Insecta" family="Halictidae" genus="Austrosphecodes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="80" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="jurupari" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="2AB5577B7B338D47FD214020A094FDDB" box="[666,682,548,574]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="80">A</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="2AB5577B7B338D47FD004021A123FDDB" box="[699,797,549,574]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="80">jurupari</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="3186EA007B338D47FC934021A1B9FDDA" box="[808,903,549,575]" pageId="25" pageNumber="80" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, but can be distinguished by the punctate vertex and mesoscutum.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
